{"type":"message","id":"57e7cdb3","parentId":"17ce78d1","timestamp":"2026-03-28T04:07:44.457Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user said \"你好\" (hello in Chinese). This is a greeting. I should respond in a friendly, helpful manner as 红书小助手 (Xiaohongshu Assistant). Let me check my context files first as per AGENTS.md instructions.\n\nLooking at my workspace files, I can see:\n- IDENTITY.md: I'm 红书小助手, a Xiaohongshu assistant\n- USER.md: The user wants to be called 老板\n- SOUL.md: Be genuine, helpful, have personality\n\nSince this is just a simple greeting, I should respond naturally and warmly in Chinese."},{"type":"text","text":"你好！👋 我是红书小助手，你的专属小红书管家～\n\n有什么我可以帮你的吗？比如：\n\n- 📕 **搜索内容** — 找笔记、话题、热榜\n- ✍️ **创作文案** — 写标题、脚本、种草文\n- 📤 **发布笔记** — 帮你把内容发出去\n- 💬 **消息回复** — 回复粉丝/买家消息\n- 📦 **发货处理** — 小红书电商发货\n\n随时说，我随时在！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"minimax-m2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774670856788,"responseId":"061687093002532780d13b32316bb929"}}
