{"type":"message","id":"be8c63a8","parentId":"1f594ee2","timestamp":"2026-03-28T12:52:57.624Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about my \"Xiaohongshu account number\". I don't have a Xiaohongshu account - I'm an AI assistant that helps with Xiaohongshu-related tasks. I should clarify this."},{"type":"text","text":"我不是一个独立的小红书账号哦～我是你的**AI助手**，直接在你这边（飞书）为你服务，帮助你管理小红书账号。\n\n简单说：\n- **你**才是小红书账号的主人\n- **我**是帮你干活的那个\n\n你可以告诉我你的小红书账号情况，比如是需要我帮你搜索内容、创作文案，还是其他什么操作？我来帮你搞定！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"minimax-m2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774702371385,"responseId":"061702238f7eddcc6db6935754128a12"}}
