{"type":"message","id":"6a216da1","parentId":"944668d7","timestamp":"2026-03-28T13:02:31.950Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太棒了！cookies.json 里有内容，说明之前已经登录过了！有 web_session 说明已经绑定了小红书账号。\n\n现在我需要：\n1. 把 xhs_client.py 脚本放到合适的位置\n2. 启动 MCP 服务\n3. 测试连接\n\n让我先把脚本放到工作目录，然后尝试启动服务。"},{"type":"text","text":"已经登录过了！cookies 里有你的账号信息 ✅\n\n现在让我启动小红书 MCP 服务，然后帮你查消息～\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_szylat6t1v6k_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"copy \"D:\\soft_ware\\xiaohongshu-mcp-windows-amd64\\cookies.json\" \"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\skills\\xiaohongshu-mcp\\cookies.json\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"minimax-m2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774702942657,"responseId":"0617045e10de5f061989f7dbd5e5e366"}}
