{"type":"message","id":"741d5934","parentId":"baad1636","timestamp":"2026-03-28T13:03:13.310Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"MCP服务已经成功启动了！显示已登录。现在让我调用检查消息的功能。但是看了一下脚本，目前只有搜索、详情、发布等功能，没有专门查看消息的功能。不过cookies.json里有一个\"unread\"字段，包含了未读消息数量。让我看看能不能通过MCP API获取消息。\n\n让我尝试获取消息列表。从cookies里我看到有个unread字段：`\"unread\":\"{%22ub%22:%2269aecf200000000015030960%22%2C%22ue%22:%2269c136880000000023007037%22%2C%22uc%22:52}\"`\n这个解码后是 `{\"ub\":\"69aecf200000000015030960\",\"ue\":\"69c136880000000023007037\",\"uc\":52}`，其中uc:52表示52条未读消息。\n\n让我用search或者其他方式看看能不能拿到消息。不过这个MCP客户端似乎没有专门的消息API。让我看看有没有其他API端点。"},{"type":"text","text":"MCP 服务已成功启动 ✅\n\n检测到你的账号有 **52 条未读消息**！让我帮你查一下具体内容～\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_060e6qp64wfi_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\skills\\xiaohongshu-mcp\\scripts\\xhs_client.py status 2>&1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"minimax-m2.7","usage":{"input":490,"output":498,"cacheRead":34941,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35929,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774702983833,"responseId":"06170488406def6d774600be4b930190"}}
