{"type":"message","id":"201cb93a","parentId":"9978b69a","timestamp":"2026-03-28T13:05:08.586Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The MCP server doesn't seem to have message/chat endpoints exposed. Let me look at the xhs_client.py more carefully to see what endpoints are actually available.\n\nActually, looking at the xhs_client.py code, it has:\n- /api/v1/login/status\n- /api/v1/feeds/search\n- /api/v1/feeds/detail\n- /api/v1/feeds/list\n- /api/v1/publish\n- /api/v1/note/delete\n\nThere's no message/chat endpoint. The MCP tool is primarily for content creation and search, not for messaging/chat.\n\nHowever, I notice from the cookies that there's an \"unread\" field with 52 unread messages. This might be comments on notes rather than direct messages.\n\nLet me be honest with the user - the xiaohongshu-mcp tool doesn't currently support reading or replying to messages. It's designed for content creation (publishing notes) and searching, not for messaging.\n\nI should let the user know this limitation and suggest alternatives."},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉，我仔细看了这个 MCP 服务的接口，它目前**只支持：**\n\n✅ 已实现：\n- 搜索笔记\n- 查看笔记详情\n- 获取推荐内容\n- 发布笔记\n- 删除笔记\n\n❌ **不支持：**\n- 读取消息/私信\n- 自动回复消息\n\n这个工具主要是为了**内容创作**设计的，不是为了客服消息回复。\n\n---\n\n**如果你需要自动回复小红书消息，有几个方案：**\n\n1. **xianyu-auto-reply（闲鱼自动回复）** — 我看到你之前配置过类似的东西，但它主要是针对闲鱼的\n\n2. **浏览器自动化** — 用浏览器控制工具模拟操作，但这种方式不太稳定\n\n3. **其他 MCP 服务** — 可能需要找找有没有专门的小红书客服消息工具\n\n---\n\n你要先试试**搜索小红书内容**或**帮你写文案**吗？这些我可以直接帮你做 ✅\n\n或者如果你找到了专门的小红书消息 MCP 工具，告诉我地址我可以帮你集成～"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"minimax-m2.7","usage":{"input":336,"output":636,"cacheRead":36285,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37257,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774703088592,"responseId":"061704f133206c62138d6f8d2e8655f3"}}
